          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into thin wedges</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1721908369154-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
