            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Drain and pat your <strong>mozzarella</strong> dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!), then tear into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>crumbled Greek cheese</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>Mediterranean seasoning </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Greek cheese toastie mix</strong></p>",
