      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 10-15 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and carefully remove the<strong> cooked pepper half[ves]</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for a final 10-15 min or until the fries are crispy and golden brown</p><p>Top each <strong>cheesy ciabatta base[s] </strong>with a <strong>cooked pepper half</strong>, hollow side down</p><p>Place a <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>on top – this is your<strong> Greek cheese ciabatta[s]</strong></p>",
