    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> Greek cheese ciabatta[s] </strong>and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (eg. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 4-5 min per side, checking occasionally or until the ciabatta is golden and the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>Greek grilled cheese & pepper toastie</strong></p>",
